<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='290385' id='t-290385'>to do something with it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='292220' id='t-292220'>you wouldn't be grateful for it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='295149' id='t-295149'>Opportunity is the gift within every gift,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='299169' id='t-299169'>and we have this saying,
opportunity knocks only once.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='305943' id='t-305943'>Well, think again.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='308679' id='t-308679'>Every moment is a new gift,
over and over again,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='312890' id='t-312890'>and if you miss the opportunity
of this moment,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='316158' id='t-316158'>another moment is given to us,
and another moment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='320175' id='t-320175'>We can avail ourselves
of this opportunity,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322889' id='t-322889'>or we can miss it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='324760' id='t-324760'>and if we avail ourselves
